quran[10{c,v,t}:
16,119,Albata jin logon ne jahalat ki bana par bura amal kya aur phir tauba kar ke apne amal ki islaah kar li to yaqeenan tauba o islaah ke baad tera rab unn ke liye ghafoor aur Raheem hai
16,120,"waqea yeh hai ke ibrahim apni zaat se aik poori ummat tha, Allah ka Mutee farmaan aur yak so woh kabhi mushriq nah tha"
16,121,Allah ki nematon ka shukar ada karne wala tha Allah ne is ko muntakhib kar liya aur seedha rasta dekhaya
16,122,duniya mein is ko bhalai di aur akhirat mein woh yaqeenan salheen mein se hoga
16,123,phir hum ne tumhari taraf yeh wahi bhaije ke yak so ho kar ibrahim ke tareeqay par chalo aur woh mushrikon mein se nah tha
16,124,"raha sabt, to woh hum ne unn logon par musallat kya tha jinhon ne is ke ehkaam mein ikhtilaaf kya, aur yaqeenan tera rab qayamat ke roz un sab baton ka faisla kar day ga jin mein woh ikhtilaaf karte rahay hain"
16,125,"ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, apne rab ke rastay ki taraf dawat do hikmat aur umdah nasiyaat ke sath, aur logon se mobahisa karo aisay tareeqa par jo behtareen ho tumhara rab hi ziyada behtar jaanta hai ke kon is ki raah se bhatka howa hai aur kon raah raast par hai"
16,126,aur agar tum log badla lau to bas isi qader le lau jis qader tum par zayad-ti ki gayi ho lekin agar tum sabr karo to yaqeenan yeh sabr karne walon hi ke haq mein behtar hai
16,127,"ae Muhammad Sallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, sabr se kaam kiye jao aur tumhara yeh sabr Allah hi ki tofeq se hai inn logon ki harkaat par ray nj nah karo aur nah un ki chaal bazyon par dil tang ho"
16,128,Allah unn logon ke sath hai jo taqwa se kaam letay hain aur ahsaan par amal karte hain
